{"tid":2095524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★兩間公屋？男患者於坪石邨玉石樓居住，張竹君又指：患者報稱居於朗屏邨","createTime":"2020-07-05T13:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T15:59:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6f5a675d65b9c412843c08cfb87a3b21d41450e6","tid":2095524,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"張竹君指，該患者發病時仍有數天上班，具傳染性，故會為食肆員工留樣本。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男患者本人於坪石邨玉石樓居住</span>，今晚會有人員派樣本瓶予居民。衞生署亦建議，倘有食客曾於6月28日後，到過彬記食肆，都可去玉石樓領取樣本瓶，當局會派發兩、三日。張竹君又指，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">患者報稱居於朗屏邨</span>，但過去幾個月已無回家，近日一直住在坪石邨玉石樓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/494223/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%A1%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E5%B0%87%E5%88%B0%E5%9D%AA%E7%9F%B3%E9%82%A8%E7%8E%89%E7%9F%B3%E6%A8%93%E6%B4%BE%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC%E7%93%B6-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1-%E9%98%B2%E4%B8%8D%E5%8B%9D%E9%98%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F494223%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25A1%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%259D%25AA%25E7%259F%25B3%25E9%2582%25A8%25E7%258E%2589%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2593%25B6-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258B%259D%25E9%2598%25B2&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3wsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=652ef79f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%